Syria Is Training Bahraini Opposition, King Tells Telegraph

-- B y   C a r o l i n e   A l e x a n d e r
-- 
2011-12-13T13:00:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/syria-is-training-bahraini-opposition-king-tells-telegraph.html
Syria  is training Bahraini
opposition figures, the Gulf island state’s King Hamad bin Isa
al-Khalifa said in an interview with the U.K.’s Telegraph
newspaper.  “We have evidence that a number of Bahrainis who oppose
our government are being trained in Syria,” he said in  the
interview  published today. “I have seen the files and we have
notified the Syrian authorities, but they deny any
involvement,” he said, giving no further details.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
Caroline Alexander in London at 
 calexander1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  